This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with face sketch synthesis and recognition. It may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category as it involves digital entertainment applications. Additionally, the use of image quality assessment metrics suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the potential law enforcement applications suggest that it could also belong to the cryptography and security (cs.CR) sub-category.
